@startuml
[*] --> StartSale
StartSale --> AddItem: Customer selects item
AddItem --> AddItem: Customer adds another item
AddItem --> Payment: All items added
Payment --> CompleteSaleWithCash: Customer pays with cash
CompleteSaleWithCash --> EndSale
EndSale --> [*]
Payment --> VerifyPayment: Customer chooses to pay by card or check
VerifyPayment --> CompleteSale: Payment is approved
CompleteSale --> EndSale
EndSale --> StartSale: Next customer arrives

@enduml
